evidence: Another major strength is speed. Ultrasound provides images in real time

triples.evidence: Ultrasound imaging involves no ionizing radiation.

evidence: Ultrasound imaging has several clear advantages. First, it involves no ionizing radiation. That's very important because, unlike X-rays or gamma rays, ultrasound uses mechanical sound waves, not electromagnetic radiation.
